{"tid":1888711,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★小西灣確診夫婦女兒IFC Longchamp上班 須關門消毒","createTime":"2020-02-20T11:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T11:05:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"da925d70344b52cf391cf5474e396f3b7f9982f2","tid":1888711,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:04:40.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒疫情持續，本港累計確診個案至68宗。《香港01》記者接獲國際金融中心（IFC）管理處今日（20日）向商戶發出的電郵，指商場內的法國品牌Longchamp店有一名前線銷售員的父母昨日確診，而該名銷售員並無出現症狀，病毒測試呈陰性，並按衞生署指令正接受14天隔離。IFC指，該店今日不營業，會進行清潔消毒。翻查資料，該店員的父母，是昨日確診公布、居於小西灣邨的夫婦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/437463/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B0%8F%E8%A5%BF%E7%81%A3%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92ifc-longchamp%E4%B8%8A%E7%8F%AD-%E9%A0%88%E9%97%9C%E9%96%80%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F437463%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592ifc-longchamp%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%258F%25AD-%25E9%25A0%2588%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%25AF%2592&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=526925ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/437463/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B0%8F%E8%A5%BF%E7%81%A3%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92ifc-longchamp%E4%B8%8A%E7%8F%AD-%E9%A0%88%E9%97%9C%E9%96%80%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92</a>"},{"pid":"707d0893e988a133d13c9e57790568b8e7bd72b0","tid":1888711,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:04:54.000Z","msg":"ifc<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e99ad3b1cc7ba734b6383468f7d5bbf1109039d","tid":1888711,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"IFC購物中心會進行清潔消毒，包括特定商店場所，所有公共區域如自動扶梯、電梯大堂、走廊、廁所等，並指自1月29日通函中的預防措施仍在全面執行，會與衛生防護中心密切合作，籲租戶提醒員工保持良好個人衛生，如果有發燒或其他呼吸道症狀，應立即就醫，避免上班。"}]}